metadata.name: 兔 The Moon
metadata.description:
This is an exclusive F&F airdrop to those who have loved & supported me throughout my entire web3 journey, thank you! 

There will only be 178 pieces in existence airdropped signifying “一起发“ which translates to prosper together. 

I have created this art piece drawing inspiration from the Rabbit zodiac, WEB3 culture, along with my signature “puke” and “rainbow” traits. I have also chosen to include the blessing “兔飞猛进” wishing WGMI to everyone and all ventures 兔 the moon.
